543
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,560
The bugs.

544
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:08,440
They drive me crazy.

545
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:16,360
Let me guess. Bambi.

546
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:19,600
Fox told me to wait out here while
